featured_reviews.review_translated_text: This mosque is located right in the market in Chaibasa city of Sadar Bazar in West Singhbhum district of Jharkhand. This mosque is small but being in the middle of the city gives great comfort to the worshipers and even on the day of Jumma, people close their shops and offer namaz here. You are also in Chaibasa and it is time for Namaz, so you can reach here in 5 minutes and offer Namaz.
